                <h1>Unlocking Game Theory: Strategies for Competitive Success</h1>
                <p>Game theory is a mathematical framework used to analyze strategic interactions among rational decision-makers. It explores how individuals or groups can optimize their outcomes in competitive situations, including economics, politics, and social behavior. By understanding strategies, players can predict others' actions and improve their own decisions.</p>
